<div class="container">
    <h2>Welcome to our Login System Project!</h2>
    <h3>Step by step guide to use this system:</h3>
    <ol>
      <li>Create an account by clicking on the <u>"Log in"</u> button and then <u>"No account? Create one"</u> .</li>
      <li>Fill in the required information in the registration form.</li>
      <li>Submit the form to create your account.</li>
      <li>Also you can create your account with Google.</li>
      <li>Once your account is created, you can log in using your credentials.</li>
      <li>After successful login, you can visit your profile page.</li>
      <li>If you don't log in successfully, you can not visit profile page.</li>
      <li>In profile page you can "Update you password" , "log from this device" , "log out from all device".</li>

      <li>If you forgot your password you can generate password reset link by clicking on the "<u>Log in</u>" button and then "<u>Reset password</u>" .</li>
      <li>Make sure to log out when you are done using the system to ensure the security of your account.</li>
    </ol>
    <p>Enjoy using our Login System!</p>
